551
00:51:14,905 --> 00:51:16,323
Don't you have a conscience?

552
00:51:16,907 --> 00:51:18,825
You and Jun-su aren't the same.

553
00:51:20,452 --> 00:51:21,745
You're not him.

554
00:51:22,704 --> 00:51:24,164
